Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"February 13th"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.34,0:00:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"February 14th"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.21,0:00:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come for my chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.25,0:00:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.75,0:00:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I was promised chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.38,0:00:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're talking about Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.46,0:00:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that. Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.67,0:00:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd you hear that from?\NDo we even have any chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.30,0:00:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like some chocolate from you, too, Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.17,0:00:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.67,0:00:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Sure, if you give me some, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.05,0:00:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that's how Valentine's works.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.63,0:00:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.17,0:00:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,--I think so! Take that, and that, and that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.13,0:00:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,--In that case, I shall prepare some\Nfor you the next time we meet!\N--I think so! Take that, and that, and that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.09,0:00:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yipee!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.34,0:00:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.38,0:00:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This happens every time, so there's\Na part of me that just expects it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.00,0:00:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.67,0:01:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Does tomorrow work for you?\NCan you still hang out?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.67,0:01:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,"I sure can."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.88,0:01:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Will this work out?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.55,0:01:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Shimamura started hibernating\Nin her {\i1}kotatsu {\i0}and won't come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.34,0:01:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Kay, thanks!"\N"Sure!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.25,0:01:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Kay, thanks!"\N"Sure!"\N"Morning!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.84,0:01:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Morning!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.96,0:01:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Heya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.84,0:03:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,--Just one look at Shimamura warms my heart.\NNo wonder she's my sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.30,0:03:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,--We have an English quiz today, don't we?\N--Just one look at Shimamura warms my heart.\NNo wonder she's my sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,--Ayup.\N--Just one look at Shimamura warms my heart.\NNo wonder she's my sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,--Yup.\N--Just one look at Shimamura warms my heart.\NNo wonder she's my sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,--You two seem confident.\N--Just one look at Shimamura warms my heart.\NNo wonder she's my sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.21,0:03:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured if I kept calling her that,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,--it'd eventually be less embarrassing,\Nbut it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,--Let me see your notes later.\N--it'd eventually be less embarrassing,\Nbut it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.59,0:03:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... Chocolate already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.05,0:03:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought it, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.63,0:03:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. I get it, but now I feel like\NI'm being told to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...basically Shimamura's puppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:04:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But I mean, if I was a pup,\Nmaybe Shimamura would hold me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I could curl up on her lap...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.13,0:04:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And she'd do all kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.84,0:04:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Being Shimamura's pup would be like the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.80,0:04:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been pretty unfortunate up until now,\Nbut now I know for certain...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.55,0:04:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm actually pretty stupid lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.84,0:04:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to go hang out now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there somewhere you wanted to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I want to go to Nagoya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.75,0:04:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Er... Um... Is that a bit too far?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.38,0:04:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagoya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, so that's how this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.09,0:04:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.59,0:04:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.09,0:05:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been wanting to go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So what are we going to do in Nagoya, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.67,0:05:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.96,0:05:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Buy some chocolate.\NUm... I haven't bought any yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.84,0:05:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I just thought it'd be fresher\Nif I bought some the day of...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.05,0:05:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, I see. Well, that's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? Maybe Shimamura's\Nmore excited than I thought she'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.38,0:05:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time I see her smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.42,0:05:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, your chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't get to see it until you buy yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.84,0:05:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If I gave you yours now, it wouldn't\Nbe an exchange, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I really am just Shimamura's puppy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way, Adachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.96,0:05:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to change into\Nyour Chinese dress today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:05:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinese dress?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.34,0:06:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, like you did on Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd rather have me wear that,\NI'll go change...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.34,0:06:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, if you want me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, I mean, we don't want to leave too late...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Limited Express"      "Toyohashi"\NSpecial Rapid Train"   "Toyohashi"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.92,0:06:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! We'll make the train if we run.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.42,0:06:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.75,0:06:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now time for a breather.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprise you knew the transfer time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.42,0:06:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,--The train bound for Toyohashi\Nis now departing from lane four.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.34,0:06:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,--Hurry, Adachi!\N--The train bound for Toyohashi\Nis now departing from lane four.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be careful of the closing doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We made it... Though just barely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's an open seat. Just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you take it, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you can have it, Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.84,0:07:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you should sit, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.00,0:07:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You were sleeping during class.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.42,0:07:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.84,0:07:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you really were asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.09,0:07:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay, I guess I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Does... my face look weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.67,0:07:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.71,0:07:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.96,0:07:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.67,0:07:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So... It's about 20 minutes to Nagoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.09,0:07:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty boring until then, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah... Then why don't we play {\i1}shiritori{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:07:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shiritori{\i0}? Nice. In that case... Apple [{\i1}ringo{\i0}]!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.42,0:08:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Go? Go... {\i1}Gomoku {\i0}soba{\i1}.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.67,0:08:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, you are a kid, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.63,0:08:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ba... Ba... Basketball [{\i1}basuketobooru{\i0}].
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ru... Ru... {\i1}Ruibe{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ruibe{\i0}? Seriously, Adachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I... Ice cream [{\i1}aisu{\i0}].
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Su... Su... Su...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.42,0:08:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Five... Four...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Su?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Love [{\i1}suki{\i0}].
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.50,0:08:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,--Two... One.\N--Su... Su... Sugyaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.88,0:08:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Su... Su... Su... Sugakiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you just said it too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Sugakiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:09:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagoya, Nagoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.42,0:09:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please make sure to take all of your...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.30,0:09:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, there's a huge line.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I line up, I'm just going\Nto make you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.75,0:09:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.46,0:09:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... There's still time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So what should we do next to kill some time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.75,0:09:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Um... M-Maybe thumb wrestle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.67,0:09:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Eleven victories and three losses. I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.92,0:09:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, thumb wrestling can get pretty heated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.92,0:09:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.88,0:09:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura seems to be all smiles today,\Nwhich is throwing me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:09:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time I see her smile,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.67,0:10:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to stop my cheek muscles\Nfrom relaxing into a dumb expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.55,0:10:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So here's the big reveal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go. Your Valentine's chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually bought some from here yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"February 14th"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.55,0:10:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"February 13th"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.55,0:10:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Heya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.21,0:10:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening. Wait, I guess it's still hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.00,0:10:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you have something you wanted to shop for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.63,0:10:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.96,0:10:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Do you have a boyfriend, Shima?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.84,0:10:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just getting some to give to a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:11:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The train bound for Toyohashi\Nis about to depart from lane four.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.63,0:11:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be careful of the closing doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.55,0:11:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We just made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, just barely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.05,0:11:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like there's one seat open.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.13,0:11:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.25,0:11:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,--Why don't you take it?\N--Why don't you sit, Shima?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I guess I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.50,0:11:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.50,0:11:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So... You're in high school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.71,0:11:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you see my uniform and bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.80,0:11:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.09,0:11:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess you're in high school, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.13,0:11:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah. Have you actually\Nbeen going to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.13,0:12:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhat. Looks like you need\Nto redye your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.84,0:12:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I've been trying to decide\Nwhat to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.59,0:12:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.75,0:12:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Shima...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.88,0:12:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you call me when we were little?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Shima! Shima!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.50,0:12:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.67,0:12:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.67,0:12:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.50,0:12:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Shima, you've really changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.50,0:12:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.38,0:13:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Change is an understatement.\NI was basically a stranger before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to be insanely cheerful, super friendly,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.59,0:13:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,dumb, and free...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.67,0:13:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if that's what Tarumi\Nexpects me to be now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.96,0:13:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, remember when there was a murder here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There was?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.09,0:13:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't the big city scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,For real.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.13,0:13:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why being with Tarumi\Nis honestly a bit uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's slightly different,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.34,0:13:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but I sorta feel like Adachi right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.80,0:13:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Reality doesn't change\Nas gracefully as memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually bought some from here yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, reall--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.21,0:13:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway, let's exchange chocolates.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.88,0:13:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay, congrats.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.67,0:13:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Congrats?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:13:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Then, uh... Congrats.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just let them sit in your room.\NMake sure you eat them, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.17,0:14:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, then let's eat them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.17,0:14:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, now? Right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. Right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.80,0:14:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, you don't waste any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.71,0:14:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.75,0:14:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.50,0:14:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I guess you're telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.50,0:14:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a way to make her doubt me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.05,0:15:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Do you want one, Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, say, "Ah."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.84,0:15:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.42,0:15:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.80,0:15:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.25,0:15:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Just follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:15:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, there it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.00,0:16:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It should start around 6 PM...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.30,0:16:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What will?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.09,0:16:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Special Valentine's Day Promotion"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Special Valentine's Day Promotion"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's starting! Let's go, Adachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Special Valentine's Day Promotion"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.59,0:16:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"We'll share your messages"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"I love you, Kazuki!! Forever! -Makiko"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.34,0:16:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"I love you, Take! -Mizu"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"I hope we can continue to stay close"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.84,0:16:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Shima?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.05,0:16:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.80,0:16:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we head home?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.21,0:16:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we were expecting this\Nto be a lot more fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There were probably more things\Nthat should've happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.88,0:17:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But in reality, all that remains\Nis this bothersome heavy mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is probably my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"Does tomorrow work for you?\NCan you still hang out?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.17,0:17:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.75,0:17:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Does tomorrow work for you?\NCan you still hang out?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,"I sure can."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"I sure can."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.55,0:17:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to drag you around today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.13,0:17:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.09,0:17:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something so lingering.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.80,0:17:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Something incomplete.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.88,0:17:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you supposed to do at times like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you call me when we were little?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... Hrm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.17,0:18:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang it! Listen to me, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.71,0:18:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let go of the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,--People can't change that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.25,0:18:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,--Taru...\N--People can't change that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.75,0:18:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.88,0:18:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Shima!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.05,0:18:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"I hope we can continue to stay close!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.05,0:18:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My past is connected by briars,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"I hope we can continue to stay close!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,so when I try to reflect upon it,\NI'm hurt by my incomplete self from the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,so when I try to reflect upon it,\NI'm hurt by my incomplete self from the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.25,0:18:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"-Hogetsu Shimamura"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.00,0:18:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"-Hogetsu Shimamura"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.00,0:18:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There are times I want to reach into the briars.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"I hope we can continue to stay close!\N-Hogetsu Shimamura"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There are times I want to reach into the briars.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.67,0:18:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"I hope we can continue to stay close!\N-Hogetsu Shimamura"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.67,0:18:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if that means I prick myself and bleed...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.84,0:18:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"I hope we can continue to stay close!\N-Hogetsu Shimamura"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura... Wait, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.46,0:19:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There's this fortunetelling bit\Non this nightly TV program.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.75,0:19:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They were asking for entries,\Nso I tried sending it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.34,0:19:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Libra"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.59,0:19:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's lucky letter is... D!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.34,0:19:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured I'd never see it,\Nso I put something mild... Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.34,0:19:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"I hope we can continue to stay close!\N-Hogetsu Shimamura"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.34,0:19:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already over? That was fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.17,0:19:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What exactly did you mean by close?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.09,0:19:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What did I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.71,0:19:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Did you need an actual example?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.67,0:19:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just wondering, like,\Nwhat kind of direction you meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.59,0:19:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, friendship?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.25,0:19:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Yeah, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.38,0:19:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think it was perfect to see this with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:20:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was entering this thing,\Nyour face popped into my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.67,0:20:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So I tried to reflect that into my message.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.88,0:20:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's... wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.46,0:20:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.38,0:20:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.55,0:20:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, you just startled me. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.50,0:20:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, no more surprise glomps, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.46,0:20:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.05,0:20:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I can then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.80,0:20:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So... If I ask you first,\Nit's okay, to uh, do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.67,0:21:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You want to hug me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.09,0:21:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.30,0:21:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Well... Because it's warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.34,0:21:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Let's warm up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.88,0:21:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever! Come get some! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.42,0:21:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I guess this is one way to get closer...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.30,0:22:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Though you're so skinny, Adachi,\Nthat neither one of us are going to get warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.92,0:22:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if everyone around us\Nthought we were weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.88,0:22:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Were they laughing at us?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.38,0:22:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I could only see Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.59,0:22:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Any place I could do that made it the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.09,0:22:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Episode 9: 'Love That Embraces\Nthe Holy Mother: Marigold'"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.80,0:22:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Episode 9: 'Love That Embraces\Nthe Holy Mother: Marigold'"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.80,0:22:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.05,0:22:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Episode 9: 'Love That Embraces\Nthe Holy Mother: Marigold'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.96,0:23:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time: 'Cherry Blossoms and\NSpring and Spring and the Moon'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.80,0:23:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time: 'Cherry Blossoms and\NSpring and Spring and the Moon'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.80,0:23:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Adashimapedia: Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.84,0:23:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time: 'Cherry Blossoms and\NSpring and Spring and the Moon'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.84,0:23:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagafuji's Butcher Shop is doing\Na Valentine's Day promotion, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.34,0:23:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You selling chocolate-filled croquettes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.88,0:23:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing that cliché.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.55,0:24:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Grab your boy's heart with\Na special on actual hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.17,0:24:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How would you feel getting offal from a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.34,0:24:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's fire up that grill!
